{"tid":1376660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港巴打示威戰術的進化討論","createTime":"2019-07-28T11:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:24:52.000Z","uid":265094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50a2613660f5df841d1747011e4db348b73fce02","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"相信大家都清楚，要長期堅持，係須要有戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一要有盾陣，包括我地以前係用遮，後來用浮板，而架用木板！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPPPgLM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPPPgLM.png&h=1973ad25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浮板最輕，可以擋到一般攻擊，似乎最岩用！<br />\n<br />\n第二樣係應付催淚，大家都發現用水淋熄佢係最有用方法，所以我諗到如果用兩個大漏斗，幼個邊兩個咀上下搏返實，咁就可以令大家好容cup住個催淚彈，而且好易倒水入去！<br />\n<br />\n以上兩點係想大家可以有效d保護自己！<br />\n<br />\n第三樣係，元朗白衫爆徒件事後，我見有人用呢樣野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhNhqF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhNhqF2.png&h=86794ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家小心，殺傷力可以好大，而且好平就買得到，可能d白衫有大把，所以大家要小心點！"},{"pid":"f07b5c09fa31b505ed8b4f8dd1e99ae9c77606e5","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安，希望大家真係平平安安，反對暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afc24d4f3e83c146bfb57e7a3b32a18f59d9b34","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"戰術定裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbc8a4e9e2d637da25f6386066b6f52f11a7d83","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3afc24d4f3e83c146bfb57e7a3b32a18f59d9b34","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:37:08.000Z","msg":"戰術定裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"先講裝備先，最貼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3a4a0afaaab7a27ef4584a7afcf92c91e69a0f","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"推<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2e51746ae57990cbd027449e6c5b9afba2af662b","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"打又好 比人捉又好，攻擊佢地下盤/擾亂佢地步速係最好<br />\n<br />\n打亂節奏係好有用"},{"pid":"f72b0424312a35b350d0ae7160aa6cf48ef3345f","tid":1376660,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6ca55e78d7d83457a1c7a9b64226015c4744fa18","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e51746ae57990cbd027449e6c5b9afba2af662b","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"打又好 比人捉又好，攻擊佢地下盤/擾亂佢地步速係最好<br />\n<br />\n打亂節奏係好有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"咁要做好多路障"},{"pid":"9550507ad5d77a920a3b7aa17386a70b3670c9bc","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e51746ae57990cbd027449e6c5b9afba2af662b","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"打又好 比人捉又好，攻擊佢地下盤/擾亂佢地步速係最好<br />\n<br />\n打亂節奏係好有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"用咩打下盤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498d27b76ee6ab4f13aaa71a98d641c589180c95","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9550507ad5d77a920a3b7aa17386a70b3670c9bc","tid":1376660,"uid":265094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e51746ae57990cbd027449e6c5b9afba2af662b","tid":1376660,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"打又好 比人捉又好，攻擊佢地下盤/擾亂佢地步速係最好<br />